snippet.title: Old Steve Rogers Gives Shield to Sam Wilson - "How Does It Feel?" - Avengers: Endgame Ending Scene
snippet.description:
Old Steve Rogers/Captain America Gives His Vibranium Shield to Falcon/Sam Wilson - "I'll Do My Best" - Captain America and Peggy Carter Dance - Ending Scene - Avengers: Endgame (2019) Movie Clip HD [1080p]

Old Steve Rogers : How does it feel?
Sam Wilson : Like it's someone else's.
Old Steve Rogers : It isn't.
Sam Wilson : Thank you. I'll do my best.
